author: RTÉ News
title: Macron extends France's lockdown until 11 May
description: French President Emmanuel Macron has announced he is extending a virtual lockdown to curb the coronavirus outbreak until 11 May, adding that progress had been made but the battle not yet won.
content:
French President Emmanuel Macron has announced he is extending a virtual lockdown to curb the coronavirus outbreak until 11 May, adding that progress had been made but the battle not yet won.
